GAL16V8
ROM_YM

NC A15 A14 A0 HALT RW PHI2 NC NC GND
NC NC NC NC YMLE PHI2OUT BC1 BDIR ROMCE VCC

PHI2OUT = PHI2
BDIR = /A15 * A14 * /RW * HALT * PHI2
BC1 = /A15 * A14 * /RW * /A0 * HALT * PHI2
YMLE = /A15 * A14 * /RW * HALT * PHI2
/ROMCE = A15 * RW
       + A14 * RW

DESCRIPTION

Atari 7800 YM2149 Address Decoder.
ROM enabled for reads at $4000-$FFFF (48KB with 27C512, JP1=R, JP2=R).
  $4000-$7FFF reads  -> ROM (16KB window, A14=1, A15=0)
  $8000-$FFFF reads  -> ROM (32KB window, A15=1)
  $4000-$4001 writes -> YM2149 (RW=0, ROM_CE not asserted)
Supports 16KB (27C128), 32KB (27C256), and 48KB (27C512) via JP1/JP2.
